name: Awareness of Verbal Harassment
description: one of the common harassment is whistling to tease, Maybe you think whistling is a trivial & normal thing to do. But what you don't know is that whistling is a form of verbal abuse when it's used to seduce women. 'Cat-calling' can be ensnared in articles 289 - 296 of the Indonesian Criminal Code. Because this includes things that violate the sense of decency.
